At iAmIT Career Compass, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our readers. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our newsletter and related services.

Information We Collect

We may collect information about you when you sign up for and use our newsletter, including your name and email address. We may also collect information about your location and how you use our newsletter.

How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect to provide and improve our newsletter and related services. This may include using your information to personalize your experience, communicate with you, or to send you updates and newsletters.

Sharing Your Information

We will not sell or rent your information to third parties. We may share your information with third parties in limited circumstances, such as when complying with legal obligations, preventing fraud or abuse, or to protect the rights, property, or safety of our readers or others.

Your Choices

You have the right to opt out of receiving emails from us at any time. You can do this by clicking the "unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any email you receive from us or by contacting us directly.

Changes to Our Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for the latest information on our privacy practices.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at arms.patel@gmail.com.
